ferred archive. Upon extraction, a single directory named "SPACER" will be created. SPACER can be immediately run using </font>						<p><font color=#006600><code>java -jar SPACER.jar fasta_file</code>.</font>						<p><font color=#006600> See the includedREADME for more information. </font>						<ul>							<li><a href="SPACER.zip">SPACER.zip</a></li>							<li><a href="SPACER.tar.gz">SPACER.tar.gz</a></li>						</ul>					</td></tr></table></center></body></html>